Create a comprehensive graphic design brief including: Project Title, Background, Objective, Target Audience, Key Message, Design Elements Required (suggest email banner 600x300px, social post 1080x1080px, GIF if applicable), Specifications (JPG, PNG, GIF), Must-haves (e.g., Logo, Brand Colors - provide link to guidelines if possible: YOUR_BRAND_GUIDELINES_LINK), Things to Avoid. Output well-formatted text.

